<td align="center"><b>
<i>Macrotera sinaloana</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Timberlake, 1958&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Perdita &#40;Macrotera&#41; sinaloana </i>Timberlake, 1958</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
